@@TJvCustomNetscapeSplitter
Summary
  A splitter component.
Description
  TJvCustomNetscapeSplitter is the base class for splitter components that can draw their client area
  either as a splitter in Netscape Navigator or as a band with close, minimize and maximize buttons.
  Do not create instances of TJvCustomNetscapeSplitter. Instead, use a derived class, like
  TJvNetscapeSplitter.

